languages.en: //(0,3.870982)\\Ted Mendez, a defense funding consultant with the US military,//(3.870982,8.34352)\\is scheduled for a private demonstration of a new Kronstadt robotics project.//(8.34352,14.13162)\\Sounds like a way to get up close and personal with Robert Knox, 47.
